meta.githubCommitMessage: feat: implement task creation form and enhance task management UI

Refactor project and payment schemas; update contract handling and tenant management

- Renamed project date fields to planned_start_date and planned_end_date.
- Updated payment schema to replace payment_reference with description.
- Enhanced error handling in payment retrieval functions.
- Changed tenant_id references in user profiles and invoices to default_tenant_id.
- Removed unused fields and adjusted status transition logic in contracts.
- Added missing timestamp columns to invoices and work orders.
- Fixed RLS policies to prevent infinite recursion in tenant memberships.
- Added new columns for contract signing workflow and user profiles.
- Improved checklist service to handle missing columns and added order indexing.
